stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Acquired: Acquire
    Acquired --> Busy: Query / Tx
    Busy --> Idle: Rows关闭 / Commit / Rollback / Release
    Busy --> Broken: 网络断开或Backend终止
    Acquired --> Broken: Failover后旧连接
    Broken --> Destroyed: pgxpool检测
    Destroyed --> Constructing: 新请求或MinIdleConns
    Constructing --> Idle: 建连成功
    Constructing --> Failed: DNS/TLS/认证/数据库不可用
    Failed --> Constructing: 有界退避重试
